=678500FA"}, "display_name": "Nightmare Tag", "keywords": [], "long_description": "A multiplayer PvP Horror Experience packed full of INTENSE CHASES & JUMP SCARES! In Nightmare tag, you can either be one of the mortal humans trying to run and hide for your life, geared only with your flashgun, scanner, and a variety of surreal attachments. Or, become the blood-hungry monster to terrify your friends! Nightmare tag will have you and your friends screaming, laughing, yelling, & sweating until your headset runs out of power! \n\nBECOME THE NIGHTMARE: \n- Find & chase your friends before they escape the liminal Dreamscape!\n- Unique controller motion movement to use your claws to run, jump, and tear apart humans!\n- Track & hunt humans using your many abilities!\n- Eliminate all the humans to win as the monster\n\nRUN FOR YOUR LIFE: \n- Join your friends as you Run and Hide from the Nightmare!\n- Hide by being completely motionless, making you invisible to the monster\n- Physical Running Motion allows you to sprint when you are found and need to escape!\n- Your flashgun is your only weapon, use it to see where you're going and stun the monster!\n- Use your scanner to locate the monster, reunite with other humans, find power-ups, and find the objective.\n- Complete the objective win as the humans!\n\nMULTIPLE GAME MODES:\n- VHS Run\n- Quick Tag\n- Elimination (requires General Admission)\n- Capture the Fruit (requires General Admission)\n+ A variety of game and map settings to shake things up!\n\nGENERAL ADMISSION (IAP):\n- Unlock 6 more zones\n- Play Elimination and Capture the Fruit", "short_description": "A multiplayer PvP Horror Experience packed full of INTENSE CHASES & JUMP SCARES! In Nightmare tag, you can either be one of the mortal humans trying to run and hide for your life, geared only with your flashgun, scanner, and a variety of surreal attachments. Or, become the blood-hungry monster to terrify your friends! Nightmare tag will have you and your friends screaming, laughing, yelling, & sweating until your headset runs out of power! "}]}, "developer_name": "Grounded", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.groundedfilms.ca/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Enver Studio", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.groundedfilms.ca/vrdevelopment", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "459781504968480"}, {"id": "1023770785722696"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["HORROR", "SOCIAL"], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED_FOR_DOWNLOAD", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["MULTI_USER"], "id": "6670285176418243"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "218528594386661"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "218528594386661"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1697774400, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "218528594386661"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "8903704856409586", "version": "0.9.7.55"}, "id": "449389333794642", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5351957704917670", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8903704856409586"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "449389333